      "text": "Peter Fuchs, p. 158: "
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "33c5ae77eb62587f",
      "text": "> It has not been possible to make the word system sacrosanct as a concept: It has become, forgive this word formation, prostitutable – similar to communication, similar to holism."
